{"tid":2309632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人日日要同屋企人食lunch食到怕？","createTime":"2020-12-02T16:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T17:24:10.000Z","uid":75474,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc97cf45d4877572f818ffc4b0ce8bc2471899d","tid":2309632,"uid":75474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"今年fg半年無野撈 日日都喺屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆就番shift 基本上一個星期有五日下晝都喺屋企<br />\n日日12點幾就嘈醒我出去食lunch 同佢講煮個麵食 佢又唔鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔想起身 話明唔想同佢食又唔係太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出去食又黎黎去去都係食嗰兩三間茶記<br />\n一邊同自己講 唉當陪下佢老人家啦<br />\n講下講下原來已經半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陪下陪下 搞到佢以為我日日都想出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假日老母唔想出街淨係食下雲吞做lunch 佢又發老脾話要出去食<br />\n仲同我老母講&rdquo;啊仔都想出去食架&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我真係食一世營多都得...<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都好怕呢啲屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4730f63c8aac25c9bec8a6c00061a7494c39b6e","tid":2309632,"uid":149278,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"襯父母健健康康行得走得時多d同佢地相處<br />\n <br />\n結婚後見既機會好少，每次返屋企都覺得佢地老左好多<br />\n<br />\n見字者父母身體健康"},{"pid":"eb872320dd20d491aa2b733a60037c0d20677f24","tid":2309632,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"好妒忌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c945e686029db816db731ec6a25ffa59c5f4fa","tid":2309632,"uid":156092,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb872320dd20d491aa2b733a60037c0d20677f24","tid":2309632,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"好妒忌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:12:37.000Z","msg":"點解 我覺得我老豆好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n管撚住<br />\n<br />\n我想出去住！"},{"pid":"3997c182b31ee6dfd462cf1e917fc991942acd0b","tid":2309632,"uid":123151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"明明就好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過其實你直接講都得嘅啫"},{"pid":"34d268a3321fa73f634246eb598d2ff3592dc266","tid":2309632,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:24:10.000Z","msg":"好好珍惜同屋企人相處嘅時間啦"}]}